Rules.InvariantScript:
Switch(
    varUserLevel ,
     "USER",
    Sort(
        col_Notification,
        Created,
        SortOrder.Descending
    ),
     "ADMIN",
    Sort(
        mngr_notify_Col,
        Created,
        SortOrder.Descending
    ),
     "SUPER-ADMIN",
    Sort(
        Filter(
            FirstN(
                NotificationList_CertificationApp,
                2000
            ),
            "has uploaded proofs" = Notification And UserDeleted = false
        ),
        Created,
        SortOrder.Descending
    )
)
